QueryType: Animal Production (Piggery, Goatery, Sheep Farming etc.)

QueryText: Asking about the management of leaf spot and rhizome rot of ginger.
KCCAns: I suggest him to spray 1 % Bordeaux mixture or Copper oxychloride 0.25% for leaf spot and to drench the affected areas with 0.3% mancozeb 75 WP(2g/l) or captaf for rhizome rot of ginger.

QueryText: Asking about the medicine for poultry
KCCAns: Advice- Ambiplex-5ml/lit. of water Ostovet-5ml/lit. of water
I suggested him to spray Dimethoate 30 EC @ 2ml/l of water
